      <title>巴尔的摩电费明年将上涨 11%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/baltimore-home-power-bills-to-jump-11-next-year-as-costs-soar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月的电网拍卖中，采购电力的成本飙升至历史最高水平，巴尔的摩地区的房主很可能会看到电费从 2025 年中期开始上涨 11%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/baltimore-home-power-bills-to-jump-11-next-year-as-costs-soar</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 23:11:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
